        <h2>âš¡ Performance Metrics</h2>
        <div class="metrics-summary">
            <span class="metric-badge good"><span>ğŸ“ˆ</span> Growth: +12%</span>
            <span class="metric-badge warning"><span>âš ï¸</span> Low Stock: 3 items</span>
